entries.femaleVariant: You asked, you received. What's the problem?
The problem's that you were late! By three whole fucking days!
I already explained. There was a sandstorm, we--
Guess what? That's none of my fucking concern.
We lost a lot of eddies because of you!
How 'bout we get this over with, Roman? We were late. Our bad, granted. We'll scratch off ten percent.
Twenty.
Who is this?!
They call me V.
Why do you need to know?
I don't give an ass-licking fuck what they call you!
They call me V.
Why do you need to know? Were you gonna ask me out?
Give me one good reason why I shouldn't rip your tongue out of your fucking cunt!
entries.maleVariant: Give me one good reason why I shouldn't rip your tongue out of your fucking dickslit!

entries.femaleVariant: Simmer down now. She's with us.
entries.maleVariant: Simmer down now. He's with us.

entries.femaleVariant: Fine, let's call it a fucking day already. I'll give the sig for the eddies.
Save us your patronizing, V. We knew the risk. But--
Fifteen.
Sorry to interrupt. How's it goin'? Close the deal yet?
Fuck... Sniper!
Don't know if there's gonna be a "later."
entries.maleVariant: I don't know if there's gonna be a "later."

entries.femaleVariant: Have it your way.
That had nothing to do with the Aldecaldos.
Good. I was starting to get a headache from all your bitching.
Kill them all!
Now, now, that had nothing to do with the Aldecaldos.
entries.maleVariant: Now, now... that had nothing to do with the Aldecaldos.

entries.femaleVariant: Said you were all together, yeah? Am I right, or did I fucking hear wrong?
Well, I'll be damned... I know you! Saw you back at the Aldecaldo camp... They call you V, right?
I came here alone.
The one and only.
Did someone from the family send you here?
Why do I get the feeling something isn't right?
Now, why do I get the feeling something's wrong? What've you gotten yourselves into?
Here by pure chance. No one sent me.
Why? Is this the kind of place I'm s'posed to be?
entries.maleVariant: Why? Is this the kind of place I'm supposed to be?

entries.femaleVariant: Carol and Cass're here to close a deal with the Scavengers... We purloined some cyberware for 'em.
And…?
And it's takin' 'em near eternity! Somethin' isn't right.
I'll go and take a look – make sure everything's OK.
I'll take a look and see what's going on.
Dealing with the scavs never ends well.
Dealin' with scavs never ends well...
Wait, wait! It's just... well, they could get real sore about--
Next time just stick to retrofitting old clunkers in the Badlands.
entries.maleVariant: Next time, just stick to retrofitting old clunkers in the Badlands.

entries.femaleVariant: Just keep a lookout.
V? What're you doin' here?!
Oh, I thought I'd drop by, y'know – make sure everyone's playin' fair.
entries.maleVariant: Thought I'd drop by, y'know – make sure everyone's playin' fair.

entries.femaleVariant: Who the fuck is this?!
Something about this deal stinks.
Deals either go quickly, or they go badly. It's biz one-oh-one.
Longer you drag out the convo, more peeps you'll drag in – just a reminder that there are more of us, case you were to pull a gonk move.
entries.maleVariant: Longer you drag out the convo, more peeps you'll drag in – just a reminder that there are more of us, in case you were to pull a gonk move.

entries.femaleVariant: You think you're so fuckin' latest, don't you? And what if I do wanna pull a gonk move starting with your ugly face?
You can try.
What're you trying to pull here, huh?! This some kinda scare tactic?
Can you count to fucking three? One, two, three! That's how many you were supposed to be!
Heap of money was also s'posed to be here. And I can't see any.
You must be outside your mind, V. Why'd you come here?
You can't trust the scavs.
Your guy outside was freaking out.
You can't trust the scavs. Nothing ever ends well with them.
I could smell the trap from a mile away.
Bumped into your man outside. Said it was takin' too long, so I figured I'd take a look.
Dealin' with the scavs? On their turf? On their terms? You must really be desperate.
And desperate people don't think straight.
We really need this money. Like, badly.
Hush up now! You can conversate all you want later.
Sniper. Up there behind the silo.
Damn it to heck...!
Funny.
Didn't like your ugly skinplate from the get-go. Now I know why.
You're the one who flushed us out in Watson. Sandra Dorsett. Thought we'd forget, huh?
We're done here.
I'd think real hard about your next move.
If I were you, I'd think real hard about your next move.
You're right – I was the one who took out your chooms in Watson. Shot 'em like fish in a barrel.
entries.maleVariant: 'Cause you're right – I was the one who took out your chooms in Watson. Shot 'em all like fish in a barrel.

entries.femaleVariant: Why do you think this'll play out any different? 'Cause you got us surrounded?
entries.maleVariant: So why do you think this'll play out any different? 'Cause you got us surrounded?

entries.femaleVariant: Cause you put some dipshit with a sniper on a roof?
entries.maleVariant: Cause you put some dipshit with a sniper rifle on a roof?

entries.femaleVariant: Take a look at me. A real good one. You see my implants? I could slice you into ribbons 'fore you can squeeze a trigger. I know it. You know it.
Agh... Give 'em the eddies.
What, are you fucking deaf?! I said give 'em the eddies!
This isn't over yet, merc.
Well, I'll be damned... I know you! Saw you back at the Aldecaldo camp. They call you V, right?
The one and only.
Did someone from the family send you here?
I came here alone.
Why do I get the feeling something isn't right?
Now, why do I get the feeling something's wrong? What've you gotten yourselves into?
Here by pure chance. No one sent me.
entries.maleVariant: I'm here by pure chance. No one sent me.

entries.femaleVariant: Why? Is this the kind of place I'm supposed to be?
Carol and Cass are here to close a deal with the Scavengers. W-we purloined some cyberware for them...
And...?
And it's takin' 'em near eternity! Something isn't right.
I'll go and take a look – make sure everything's OK.
Wait, it's just... well, they could get real sore about--
Just keep a lookout.
I'll take a look and see what's going on.
Dealing with the scavs never ends well.
Dealin' with scavs never ends well...
entries.maleVariant: Dealin' with the scavs never ends well...

entries.femaleVariant: Next time just stick to retrofitting old clunkers in the Badlands.
Oh no, we're done. Fuck 'em up!
Okay, but...
